BlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015156, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O the Director of all affairs; O the Resurrector of all those in graves; O He Who causes oceans to flow; O He Who made the iron pliant for (Prophet) David; (Please) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad (mention your needs…) this very night; this very night.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay kaamo ko manzoom karne waale, ay qabro’n se utha khada karne waale, ay dariyaawo’n ko rawaa’n karne waale, ay Dawood ke liye lohe ko mom banaane waale, rehmat naazil farma sarkaar'e Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) par aur karde mere liye (haajat maange…) isi raat isi raat.", "Urdu": "اے کاموں کو منظم کرنے والے، اے قبروں سے اٹھاکر کھڑا کرنے والے، اے دریاؤں کو رواں کرنے والے، اے داؤد ؑکے لئے لوہے کو موم بنانے والے، محمدؐ وآل محمدؐ پررحمت نازل فرما اور کر دے میرے لئے یہ اور یہ میرے لئے ایسے ایسے کر دے (اپنی حاجتیں طلب کرے) اسی رات اسی رات۔", "RArabic": "YAA MO-DABBE-RAL OMOO-RE, YAA BAAE’SA MAN FIL QOBOO-RE, YAA MUJRE-YAL BOHOO-RE, YAA MOLAIY-YENAL HADEE-DE LE-DAAWOO-DA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WAF-A’L BEE KAZAA WA KAZAA AL-LAIY-LA